{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1689-07a_165","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Le Printemps glacé. Idille","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juillet 1689 (première partie) [tome 7], p. 165-175.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"Quoy que nous soyons sortis du Printemps, je ne puis me dispenser de vous parler encore de cette belle saison. Vous sçavez, Madame, qu’elle commença par un froid tres-rigoureux. Ce fut ce qui obligea une jeune Demoiselle qui ne m’est connuë que par ces Lettres L. H. D. V. à faire l’Ouvrage que je vous envoye. Ses Vers sont si bien tournez qu’ils meritent d’être vûs de tout le monde. Les Saisons passent, mais les belles choses se lisent avec plaisir en quelque temps que ce soit."],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"LE PRINTEMPS GLACÉ","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/hi/#"}},"#1":{"value":".","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"IDILLE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#2"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Printemps suivy de Flore,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des beaux jours &amp; des Zephirs,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avoit déja fait éclore","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans nos champs mille plaisirs :","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Déja par de doux ramages","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Oiseaux dans les Bocages","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chantoient leurs tendres langueurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et cessant d’estre captives,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Nayades sur leurs rives","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voyoient naistre mille fleurs.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Déja sur ces fleurs naissantes,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Bergers à leurs Amantes","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Racontoient le long du jour,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Combien la saison des glaces","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avoit couté de disgraces","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et de maux à leur amour.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin toute la Nature","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pleine d’un espoir charmant,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du retour de la verdure","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Marquoit son ravissement.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais l’Hiver impitoyable","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Rend ce plaisir peu durable,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour bannir le Printemps il revient sur ses pas.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Par ses barbares outrages","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" On revoit sur nos rivages","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Les glaçons &amp; les frimats.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’Aquilon fier &amp; terrible","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Chasse le Zephir paisible,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et ravit à nos champs leurs renaissans appas.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Depuis que sa froide haleine","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" A triomphé des beaux jours,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Les Plaisirs &amp; les Amours","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sont disparus dans la plaine.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" En retournant dans le hameau ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Chaque Berger se desespere","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De se voir arraché d’auprés de sa Bergere","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Par un changement si nouveau.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tandis que le Berger pleure","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des rigueurs de la saison,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le Laboureur à toute heure","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En tremble pour sa moisson.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voyant les Vents en furie","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Exercer leur barbarie","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Dans ses fertiles Guerets,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Troublé, remply d’épouvante,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il n’ose plus compter la recolte abondante","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui l’avoit tant flaté par ses riches aprets.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Enfin par l’horrible guerre","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le froid fait sur la terre,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout languit dans l’Univers ;","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les Côteaux déja verds,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quittant leur riante face","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour ceder à son horreur,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On ne voit plus que la trace","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Autans pleins de fureur.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Helas ! ce triste ravage","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui nous desole si fort,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est une funeste image","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des rigueurs de nostre sort.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Lors qu’aprés mille traverses,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et mille peines diverses","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous croyons n’avoir plus à former de souhaits,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Loin de voir couronner nostre perseverance,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un triste &amp; dur revers trompant nostre esperance","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rend nos chagrins plus vifs qu’ils ne furent jamais.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Tel, que l’ambition flate,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Courant aprés les honneurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quelquefois à la fin en goûte les douceurs","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un rang éminent où son pouvoir éclate.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Possedant peu son bonheur,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" La fortune qui le jouë","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" D’un inconstant tour de rouë","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sçait renverser sa grandeur.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  Un autre dans le commerce","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Fait sa gloire de blanchir ;","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sur l’espoir de s’enrichir","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il n’est Mer qu’il ne traverse.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Malgré mille affreux travaux","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Bravant les vents &amp; les ondes,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il visite les deux Mondes","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sur de fragiles Vaisseaux ;","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Et lors que sa main avare","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" A fait un nombreux amas","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De ce qui naist de plus rare","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Dans les barbares Climats,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Remply d’une douce attente","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qui le flate &amp; qui l’enchante,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il se remet sur la Mer.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Alors un fougueux orage","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ses riches Vaisseaux faisant faire naufrage,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il voit au fond des flots son espoir abismer.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[17]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[18]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Un cœur exempt des suplices","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la morne avarice, &amp; de l’ambition,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qui fait toutes ses delices","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" D’une tendre passion,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’a pas plus de repos en suivant la tendresse","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que l’Avare craintif, ny que l’Ambitieux.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" A peine ses soins &amp; ses vœux","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ont touché l’objet qui le blesse,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que de cet estat charmant","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Il passe au malheur extrême","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" De voir l’ingrate qu’il aime,","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En trahissant ses feux, courir au changement.","id":"/div/quote/#[19]/lg/l[11]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[20]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"  C’est ainsi qu’en mille manieres","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" L’aveugle &amp; bizarre destin","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sçait tourner nos plaisirs en des douleurs ameres","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Changeant tout en moins d’un matin.","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais si nos cœurs estoient sans vices,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si nous ne suivions point les folles passions,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il ne feroit sur nous, malgré tous ses caprices,","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que de foibles impressions.","id":"/div/quote/#[21]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[22]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ces Arbres dépoüillez de leurs charmans feüillages,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces Prez où l’herbe meurt, &amp; ces Ruisseaux glacez","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous donnent des leçons en leurs muets langages ;","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils ont veu sans fremir leurs appas effacez.","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Quoy que le Printemps se retire","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que l’hiver en couroux reprenant son empire","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ravisse toutes leurs beautez,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils ne succombent point sous tant de cruautez,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Dans un estat toûjours semblable","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces Chesnes resistant aux Autans irritez,","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Attendent des Zephirs le retour favorable","id":"/div/quote/#[23]/lg/l[10]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[24]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Si comme eux dans tous les revers","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Dont la fortune nous accable,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous gardions un esprit constant, inébranlable,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Attendant en repos ses changemens divers,","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Nous verrons couler nostre vie","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un estat plus doux, &amp; plus digne d’envie","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que si l’on nous rendoit Maistres de l’Univers.","id":"/div/quote/#[25]/lg/l[6]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[26]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Mais en voulant que tout réponde","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" A nos tiranniques desseins ;","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Voulant que pour remplir nos desirs les plus vains,","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" La terre s’unisse avec l’onde,","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Nous nous ferons toûjours un destin malheureux.","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si nous voulons goûter une tranquille joye,","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Profitons des plaisirs que le Ciel nous envoye,","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais ne courons jamais fortement aprés eux.","id":"/div/quote/#[27]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}}]}}}